50|$|PG 1047+003 is a post-AGB blue-white <b>subdwarf</b> <b>star,</b> {{located in}} the {{constellation}} of Sextans. The star is classed as member of the V361 Hydrae type (or also called sdBVr type) class of pulsators {{in the field of}} asteroseismology.No additional stellar companion has been detected in tight orbit or imaged around the <b>subdwarf</b> <b>star.</b>|$|E
